# Met Office DataHub API key (optional)
# Sign up at https://datahub.metoffice.gov.uk and create a key with access to:
#   - Site Specific Forecast API
#   - Severe Weather Warnings API
# IMPORTANT: this key is bundled into the APK as an asset — every install
# shares it. The 360-call/day free tier exhausts quickly with multiple users.
# Leave blank for public/Play Store builds; the app falls back to Open-Meteo.
MET_OFFICE_API_KEY=

# Base map tiles come from OpenFreeMap (https://openfreemap.org) — no key
# needed, free for commercial use at scale, no per-user account quota.
# Radar tiles come from RainViewer (https://www.rainviewer.com) — no key needed.
# Geocoding + fallback forecasts from Open-Meteo (https://open-meteo.com) — no
# key needed, per-user IP quota.
